Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:44.19,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眼差し　キラキラ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:52.43,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あまり大きくない道でもいいね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:56.97,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そして　駆け出す　飛び込む　奇跡へ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:01:00.89,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見上げる　手を振る　光へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:05.69,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}止まらない気持ちを繋いで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:08.53,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}リフレクティア
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.74,0:01:12.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揺らめく　近付く　明日へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:16.34,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でる　夢見る　未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:21.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まっさらな空　どこまでも連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:27.17,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}涙の終わり　合図に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:09.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}七彩的回路中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:13.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那无数的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:17.13,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}哪怕只是一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:21.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果在这里  我就能前进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:25.06,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}突如其来的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:29.19,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}又令我心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:37.51,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揪住心扉  一点阴影也无法消除
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:44.19,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的眼神闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:52.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算不是太宽的道路也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:56.97,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}于是  我向着奇迹冲出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:01:00.89,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抬头仰望  向着光芒挥手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:05.69,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}紧紧联系着无法停止的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:08.53,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Reflect  tear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.74,0:01:12.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}犹豫着靠近明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:16.34,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}奏响梦幻的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:21.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}带我去到崭新蓝天的任何一个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:27.17,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}作为泪水终结的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:32.52,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}叶わない願いごと　持て余して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:39.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}歩き出す　くちびる歌いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:44.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}残された気持ちへと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:49.49,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷たい雨降りかかる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:54.55,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れたいと　忘れないと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.87,0:22:59.24,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ゆらゆら廻りながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:04.33,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}沈む心　ワザと君に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.29,0:23:08.24,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm tellin' a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:14.58,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}形のない二人だがらこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:18.02,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大事にしたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:19.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}訊きたい…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:27.33,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今ここで何もかも話したら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:32.98,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}変わるのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:32.52,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遥远的心愿  难以释怀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:39.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}唇边的小调  伴我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:44.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}胸中残留的这份感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:49.49,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被冰冷的雨水淋湿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:54.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想要忘记  无法忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.87,0:22:59.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想来想去  无法决定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:04.33,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}沉寂的心  故意对你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.29,0:23:08.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}道出一句谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:14.58,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}正因为我们不会有结果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:18.02,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以对你才倍加珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:19.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我想问…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:27.33,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}假如此时此地我全都告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:32.98,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}结局可会改变？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:34.38,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,2000)\pos(580,200)}1话  我把…眼泪送出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:54.92,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\pos(460,160)}2话  我…想做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心目中的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拭去你的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  泪水拭去后那脸颊的柔软触感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:01:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却无从得知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那笑容我想画得更温馨一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为人手好像不够
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:02:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等这个完工后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什么「啊  是吗」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在装什么酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下蹲  我在做下蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊  下蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还在记帐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不一起吃掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都没法收拾餐具了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话不是这么说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她帮我们做了不少家务了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是站在那孩子一边的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个地方有位天使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能收集你的眼泪就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  我会把那些眼泪做成首饰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装饰在树上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发光的…泪之树
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  已经不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁发明的啊  引体向上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇  比吕美  真令人难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好慢啊  都落后我好几圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么那么有体力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为锻炼的方式不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怪物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎  你太色了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  野伏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那完全是大叔的眼神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那缠住少女雪白大腿的粘乎乎的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被你那缠人的视线绊倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么胡话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤浅同学真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就是那种真正的优等生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也不自高自大  很完美不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是傻瓜吗  你们明明住在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会和她一起上学  偷看她换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她对我说「呀  你真色」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会告诉小爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  真冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便看人家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在取鸡的饵料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是天空的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子明明想飞上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却被关在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可怜的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会取最高地方的食物给它的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么飞上天空  鸡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不给这只鸡吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这孩子是只不想飞的鸡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会知道那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  你也是和这只是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想飞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  头一次和我说话的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又知道我的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唾沫会飞出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确  我觉得我也知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很能飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你头脑好像很简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我诅咒你会遇到不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那家伙是A班的石动乃绘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:09:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没怎么见过她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年才搬来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然挺可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过却有着很多不妙的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说会和地底人发短信之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一吹口哨就能召唤出粉红色的大象之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是傻瓜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  如果是那家伙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被她诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石动乃绘必杀奥义  召唤悲剧的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说有人被她说「诅咒你那个变小」后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真变成没用的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找工头有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲的熟人死后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人的女儿比吕美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在去年由我家领养了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和我从小学起就是同班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美一直都很开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很在意她那张笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我诅咒你会遇到不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哀声叹气会变得不幸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连小爱你也想诅咒别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是自己喜欢才跳什么舞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是被赋予重望的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有啊  跳得一点都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是完全不可能成为麦屋舞的当家花旦的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想生在那种家里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很了不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只比我大一岁而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年也差很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这到处爬来爬去的婴儿也很能说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台词等你把脚底下的啤酒箱拿走再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家明明在担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店铺关门了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真一郎  你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三代吉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家那边的帮忙完事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是要烧着喉咙的那种来双倍浓度的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好  是可乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  拿酒来喝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟打搅你们也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  用不着…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真  上衣给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我擅自看到你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该道歉的是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…  为什么你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「呀  你真色」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是野伏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一般来说都是那种反应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「呀  你真色」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美的确寄住在我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  她一直都很低声下气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是东京的出版社
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都瞒着爸爸做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真  我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擅自拆封了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  嗯  因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得擅自拆封不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真可是这仲上家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎就是真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和仲上家没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我诅咒你会遇到不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字不是「喂」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石动乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常好的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你帮我把那个取消掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我变得不幸的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美极了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用不着那么夸奖我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不挺能飞的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能飞？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能飞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子  乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让雷轰丸也看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轰丸是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只鸡的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那飞不了的那只呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都已经决定好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲上真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲上真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狸猫干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吧  地面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轰丸飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  是这样的吧  地面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我诅咒你会遇到不幸」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒别人是把双刃剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  雷轰丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错  都是因为钻牛角尖的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石动乃绘的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}真一郎的鞋底也有蟑螂…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真坚强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很疼爱它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很伤心  非常地非常地伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石动乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把眼泪送出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.66,0:23:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有着一个使命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须取回眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的想让我代替雷轰丸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.69,0:23:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…想做什么…
